{"id":"e9b2e028d0d70cfa9e269b57d1d2de67a2c7e42e","url":"https://api3.cls.cn/share/article/2430838?os=web&sv=8.4.6&app=CailianpressWeb","title":"工信部：上半年规模以上制造业企业AI技术应用普及率超过30%","site_name":"TopHub","source":"Readhub · AI","byline":"财联社记者 付静\n                                                        2026-07-21 08:58","excerpt":"工信部：上半年规模以上制造业企业AI技术应用普及率超过30%","content_html":"<DIV class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\">\n    <section>\n        <div>\n            <p><img src=\"https://image.cls.cn/share/cailianpress.png\"></p><div>\n                <p>财联社</p>\n                <p>财经通讯社</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n            <p>打开APP</p>\n    </section>\n                    <section>10:07:57【工信部：上半年规模以上制造业企业AI技术应用普及率超过30%】</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n        <section>\n\n\n                <p>\n                        财联社7月20日电，国务院新闻办公室举行新闻发布会，介绍2026年上半年工业和信息化发展情况。工业和信息化部总工程师王卫明表示，上半年，工业和信息化领域创新能力不断增强，深化拓展人工智能+，规模以上制造业企业人工智能技术应用普及率超过30%，人工智能开源大模型全球累计下载量突破100亿次。\n                </p>\n\n\n                \n        </section>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n                        \n\n                        <section>财联社声明：文章内容仅供参考，不构成投资建议。投资者据此操作，风险自担。</section>\n\n\n                    <section>\n                        <span>2026-07-20 10:07:57</span>\n                        <span>2663774 阅读</span>\n                    </section>\n\n\n\n\n\n                <section>\n                    <a href=\"https://image.cls.cn/html/business/cooperation_671.html\">\n                        <p><span>商务合作</span>\n                            <span>\n                                <svg width=\"6\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 6 10\" version=\"1.1\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n                                    <polygon fill=\"#718db4\" points=\"4.13823912 5.31645525 0.472774495 1.51429726 1.19270413 0.820250198 5.52723951 5.31643009 1.20922557 9.79579718 0.489270794 9.1017762\" />\n                                </svg>\n                            </span>\n                        </p>\n                    </a>\n                </section>\n\n            \n\n\n            <div>\n                        \n                        <p>热门解锁</p>\n                    </div>\n\n\n            <section>\n                <p>相关阅读</p>\n                <div>\n                    <ul>\n                            <li data-id=\"2432010\">\n                                    <P data-openapplink=\"cailianpressopen://open?articleid=2432010&articletype=ordinary\" data-href=\"https://sj.qq.com/appdetail/com.lanjinger.choiassociatedpress\">\n                                                <section>超节点、超集群、TPU方案涌现 算力“拼系统”时代产业最关心Token性价比|WAIC观察</section>\n                                    </P>\n        \n                                \n        \n                                <section>\n                                                <pre>①算力“拼系统”时代，超节点、超集群已成主流方案，且已收获下游积极反应，曙光8000集群上线首周需求爆满；\n                                    ②华东首座国产TPU千卡智算集群已落成，二期规划今年9月上线投产；\n                                    ③多位产业人士关心Token性价比，而降Token成本是一项系统工程。</pre>\n                                            </section>\n        \n                                <div>\n                                    <div>\n                                        <p>23.7w+ 阅读</p>\n                                            <div data-href=\"https://sj.qq.com/appdetail/com.lanjinger.choiassociatedpress\" data-openapplink=\"cailianpressopen://open?articleid=2432010&articletype=ordinary\">\n                                                \n                                                    <p>27</p>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div data-href=\"https://sj.qq.com/appdetail/com.lanjinger.choiassociatedpress\" data-openapplink=\"cailianpressopen://open?articleid=2432010&articletype=ordinary\">\n                                                \n                                                    <p>239</p>\n                                            </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div data-id=\"2432010\">\n                                            <p>展开</p>\n                                            \n                                        </div>\n                                    <div data-id=\"2432010\">\n                                            <p>收起</p>\n                                            \n                                        </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </li>\n                            <li data-id=\"2431987\">\n                                    <P data-openapplink=\"cailianpressopen://open?articleid=2431987&articletype=ordinary\" data-href=\"https://sj.qq.com/appdetail/com.lanjinger.choiassociatedpress\">\n                                                <section>美股资金大轮动开启！高盛：AI之外，关注三大替代投资主题</section>\n                                    </P>\n        \n                                <div data-time=\"\">\n                                                    <p><img src=\"https://cdnjs.cls.cn/iav/original.png\">\n                                                            <span>财联社 卞纯</span>\n                                                        <span>2026-07-21 09:00</span>\n                                                    </p>\n                                                </div>\n        \n                                <section>\n                                                <pre>①随着近期AI交易波动持续，高盛分析师Snider及其团队看到了三大替代投资主题，这些领域可能被投资者低估；\n                                    ②他们指出，在市场轮动期间，投资者应关注“消费体验类股票、复利增长型企业，以及并购潜在标的”。\n                                    </pre>\n                                            </section>\n        \n                                <div>\n                                    <div>\n                                        <p>12.2w+ 阅读</p>\n                                            <div data-href=\"https://sj.qq.com/appdetail/com.lanjinger.choiassociatedpress\" data-openapplink=\"cailianpressopen://open?articleid=2431987&articletype=ordinary\">\n                                                \n                                                    <p>2</p>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div data-href=\"https://sj.qq.com/appdetail/com.lanjinger.choiassociatedpress\" data-openapplink=\"cailianpressopen://open?articleid=2431987&articletype=ordinary\">\n                                                \n                                                    <p>31</p>\n                                            </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div data-id=\"2431987\">\n                                            <p>展开</p>\n                                            \n                                        </div>\n                                    <div data-id=\"2431987\">\n                                            <p>收起</p>\n                                            \n                                        </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </li>\n                            <li data-id=\"2431921\">\n                                    <P data-openapplink=\"cailianpressopen://open?articleid=2431921&articletype=ordinary\" data-href=\"https://sj.qq.com/appdetail/com.lanjinger.choiassociatedpress\">\n                                                <section>贝莱德拟发逾120亿美元债券 为Meta得州数据中心提供融资</section>\n                                    </P>\n        \n                                <div data-time=\"\">\n                                                    <p><img src=\"https://cdnjs.cls.cn/iav/original.png\">\n                                                            <span>财联社 赵昊</span>\n                                                        <span>2026-07-21 04:54</span>\n                                                    </p>\n                                                </div>\n        \n                                <section>\n                                                <pre>①最新消息显示，贝莱德正计划发行超120亿美元债券，为Meta美国得州埃尔帕索的数据中心园区提供融资；\n                                    ②该融资将进一步推动今年围绕全球AI基础设施建设掀起的债券发行热潮，而大量债务融资也正不断加大科技行业债券估值压力。</pre>\n                                            </section>\n        \n                                <div>\n                                    <div>\n                                        <p>32.3w+ 阅读</p>\n                                            <div data-href=\"https://sj.qq.com/appdetail/com.lanjinger.choiassociatedpress\" data-openapplink=\"cailianpressopen://open?articleid=2431921&articletype=ordinary\">\n                                                \n                                                    <p>19</p>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div data-href=\"https://sj.qq.com/appdetail/com.lanjinger.choiassociatedpress\" data-openapplink=\"cailianpressopen://open?articleid=2431921&articletype=ordinary\">\n                                                \n                                                    <p>61</p>\n                                            </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div data-id=\"2431921\">\n                                            <p>展开</p>\n                                            \n                                        </div>\n                                    <div data-id=\"2431921\">\n                                            <p>收起</p>\n                                            \n                                        </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n            </section>\n\n            <div>\n                    <p>评论</p>\n                        \n                </div>\n\n       